Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:06.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:22.04,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:28.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:36.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:42.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:51.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:58.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:02.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:06.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:12.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:29.72,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:06.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這份真情實感　好想將它傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不沉溺於一去不返的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:22.04,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:28.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷於那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:36.63,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方應該有什麼正等待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:42.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著那未完結的故事　飛奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷著一顆真誠的心向著那千難萬險之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:51.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}張開心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:58.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循環傳遞著一個訊息　幸福就存於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:02.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下來的少許勇氣　儘管須以眼淚相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:06.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但這或許正是變強的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:12.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溫暖的迭句　想要永遠將這份珍重守護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心緒交織　感受著這其中的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以說沒有人是孤身隻影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:29.72,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片藍天下　好想將這份真情實感傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:19.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:28.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:37.80,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:46.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:49.15,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:57.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:06.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:15.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:27.03,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:19.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷揣著內心深處收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:28.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躍入未知的前方　那裡有什麼正等待著我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:37.80,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是與未來共鳴　不斷憶起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:46.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就會生出勇氣　就能變得堅強　也就不再是獨自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.03,0:22:49.15,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（讓你傾聽）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:57.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定會與你相遇　我會帶著真誠的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:06.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接夢想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:15.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與其坐擁這無限的時刻　倒不如追趕那絢爛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:27.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　總有一天會讓你傾聽那夢中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡藤岡什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題太突然  我有點兒手足無措 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…太突然了點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問喜歡什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…那是我們開學典禮那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  一時半會是完不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是忘了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值日生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我突然感到乏力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事兒吧  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能沒事兒啊  剩下的就拜託各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:43.93,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第11碗  果然不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫弗拉思科還是叫弗朗西斯科的是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp5}　{\fsp1}Elastico{\r}\N是牛尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  叫什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp1}Elastico{\fsp485}　{\fsp1}{\r}\N牛尾巴呢  是南美某個足球運動員常用的假動作的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學  身體怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個已經好了  沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊  難得你過來了  進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…藤岡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子制服啊  真可愛  真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先換上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看藤岡那反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計誤認為你因某種理由穿了千秋的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  沒穿幫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp33}　{\fsp1}churrasco{\fsp1}{\fsp13}　{\fsp1}Elastico{\r}\N還能和藤岡討論巴西燒烤和牛尾巴的共同點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是什麼玩意  我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會編出個你穿女子制服的理由幫你過關的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  夏奈她們在裡屋幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  藤岡  你也別反抗了  穿上這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是讓客人穿奇裝異服哄我開心的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也行  好好聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學學冬馬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話了  趕緊穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我穿不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  絕對不要  放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這睡覺會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  明天是清掃街道的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實今天早上就有點兒發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看果然是感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你睡被爐裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  趕緊上床休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會兒我熬粥給你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…我看是沒法去清掃街道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  其實我也想陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過又不能不去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓千秋陪著你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要不用客氣跟她說就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事  就搖這個鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午左右就會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了對了  你還是只能吃些清淡的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？啊  都能吃都能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想  多吃才恢復得快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那午飯想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你做些喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天這麼冷  砂鍋麵應該不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿果汁來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我有點兒渴了  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼能喝的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看完了  下一本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（東家三姐妹）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體怎麼樣了  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上去做飯  等著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:10:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂鍋麵到底是煮出來的還是燒出來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話了  趕緊拿過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在裝病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊  懷疑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這親姐姐說的話你都不信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要給你量個體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我去拿溫度計來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣才量得準
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過不想去掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就裝病騙我和春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事兒  我是真的…感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要睡到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹是星期天  就讓我多睡會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了今天的安排了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不帶你了啊  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  今天白天要去買春裝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上可以吃烤五花肉自助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有股可怕的寒意襲來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰能料到事情會發展到如此不可預料的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說我感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道千秋又要說些什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說買東西  我很想吃五花肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得烤五花肉自助是有期限的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯過這次機會就不知道下次是什麼時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想點辦法的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她該在準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  不快點兒換衣服就不帶你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我還有很多作業要寫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…為了晚上能痛痛快快的吃自助  得先寫完作業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊  夏奈竟會擔心作業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…這個嘛  偶爾也該認真的寫一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說我也想安心地吃五花肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…買東西就
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就拜託春香和千秋你們倆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我會在晚飯前寫完作業的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西就拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西的問題總算解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就是在晚飯前治好感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾  我還想難得能三人一起逛逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來買東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學是運動會的執行委員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是執行委員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回頭學校見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  冬木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  沒人在嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是夏奈叫我幫她買東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門開著…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！被爐裡有個鎬形頭盔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（鎬形頭盔：豎於頭盔錢的一種裝飾，像角一樣高高伸向左右兩邊） 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊…是內田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都窩在被爐裡…一不注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡被爐更不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡去床上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…那個…糟糕的是我昨天感冒過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在裝病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過不想去掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就裝病騙我和春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事兒才剛完  今天不能再說感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  內田  我感冒的事誰也別告訴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:04.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}（※同時服用多種藥物時需謹慎）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你說的都拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你們我補充了足夠的營養
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我房間把毛毯拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護嗓子需要的就是濕度  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從廚房拿熱水來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就OK了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著把被爐的溫度調到最高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣感冒能好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  要在床上好好休息才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行  不知道春香她們什麼時候回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須時刻準備著恢復平常的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要的是毅力啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅力…毅力…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買到合適的真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也給夏奈買了可愛的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  真期待五花肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也要奢侈一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望夏奈作業也寫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她肯定寫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…越來越難受了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再跟千秋說我感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她會怎麼罵我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要裝得跟平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常是什麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先全身放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般會躺著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就會想鑽進被爐裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有隻鎬形頭盔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  不是說了在被爐裡睡覺會感冒的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會感冒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音好像很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…在頭盔裡鑽太久…嗓子乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話的方式也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…在頭盔裡鑽太久…被熱暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在桌爐裡鑽太久  就這麼睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  沒事的  休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大人  千秋大人在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想近期跟藤岡做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平且和睦地了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不明原委
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是吵頭兒頭兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也差不多覺得煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡在你和春香面前不會顯露出他本來面目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其中就包含和他搞好關係的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真有一天能表明愛意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該感到厭煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道你要怎麼了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就教你一招關係惡化時的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終奧義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  最好是用不上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼叫春香和千秋就用名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻只叫我姓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家裡都是姓南的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就叫我「小夏奈」吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…不好意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  惹他生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背摔啊！摔不動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  你教的奧義毫無用處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係倒是沒惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他問我「你做什麼啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真照做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得刮過鬍子後反而變得更濃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為刮過之後會看到比較粗的根部  可能會有這感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是在毛長出來的時候會覺得全體截面面積變大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從醫學上來講  鬍子的量和其本身並沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以安心的刮掉哦
